---
import ContentPageHero from './ContentPageHero.astro';
---

<div class="grid gap-10 md:gap-12">
    <ContentPageHero eyebrow="Comparisons">
        <span slot="title">What kind of AI is GalexC?</span>
    </ContentPageHero>

    <section
        class="max-w-[46rem] border-t border-t-[rgba(120,113,108,0.14)] pt-6"
    >
        <div class="grid gap-5 text-lg leading-[1.8] text-[#4f4438]">
            <p class="m-0">
                GalexC overlaps with coding agents, autonomous harnesses, and
                other emerging AI systems, but it isn't trying to be a generic
                assistant or a pure autonomy play.
            </p>
            <p class="m-0">
                The point is a professional-grade personal AI that can do
                technical and business-related work with you and for you.
            </p>
            <p class="m-0">
                It starts from a simple idea. LLMs are incredible, but they're
                only one tool in the tool chest.
            </p>
            <p class="m-0">
                We already have other incredible, proven, and often overlooked
                technologies for memory, routing, background work, review,
                versioning, and system ownership. GalexC is about putting those
                pieces together so the result is actually useful for serious
                professional and technical work.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>
